- Optimizes for featured snippets read aloud by smart speakers
- Helps AI systems identify the most important content sections

Interlink service pages, area pages, and FAQ pages → topical authority.

Part 6: Engagement & Long-Term SEO

6.1 User Engagement

Strong above-the-fold CTA: "Get Your Free Quote in 60 Seconds".

Add related articles widget ("Carpet Cleaning Cost Guide", "How to Remove Wine Stains", "DIY vs Professional Cleaning").

Interactive tools (quote calculator, postcode checker, service area map) = higher engagement → AI finds them cite-worthy.

Blog "Updates" section refreshed monthly → freshness keeps you in Copilot's index.